"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**Black Friday Surface Pro 8 deals have arrived, browse all the best Black Friday Microsoft Surface deals on this page**\\n\\nNovember 22, 2021 08:40 AM Eastern Standard Time\\n\\nBOSTON--([BUSINESS WIRE](https://www.businesswire.com/))--Black Friday Surface Pro 8 deals for 2021 are live. Find the best offers on the Surface Pro 8 tablet and more Surface laptops. Links to the best deals are listed below.\\n\\n**Best Surface Pro 8 deals:**\\n\\n* **[Save up to $430 on Microsoft Surface Pro 8 at Walmart](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3EM47aX&esheet=52535111&newsitemid=20211122005256&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+up+to+%24430+on+Microsoft+Surface+Pro+8+at+Walmart&index=1&md5=8ab2f2f8ebd1d715c7c5a5e38b0fefe5)** - shop the latest deals on Surface Pro 8 and accessories\\n* **[Save on the latest Surface Pro 8 Intel Core i7 model at Walmart](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ECMev6&esheet=52535111&newsitemid=20211122005256&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+on+the+latest+Surface+Pro+8+Intel+Core+i7+model+at+Walmart&index=2&md5=b9077bc564bd4c8793ac993f5523a8bc)** - check live prices on the Microsoft Surface Pro 8 Intel Core i7 model which features up to 120 Hz refresh rate\\n* **[Shop the new Surface Pro 8 at Microsoft.com](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.linksynergy.com%2Fdeeplink%3Fid%3DW3aVNSp0lsg%26mid%3D24542%26murl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.microsoft.com%252Fen-us%252Fsearch%252Fresult.aspx%253Fq%253Dsurface%252Bpro%252B8&esheet=52535111&newsitemid=20211122005256&lan=en-US&anchor=Shop+the+new+Surface+Pro+8+at+Microsoft.com&index=3&md5=39253ea49f84c0e67e473c810ac2b3ae)** - the Microsoft Surface Pro 8 has a larger 13” touchscreen display and two Thunderport 4 ports for high-speed connections\\n* **[Save on the Microsoft Surface Pro 8 at Amazon.com](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fgeni.us%2FuosJ2Af&esheet=5253