rface+laptops%2C+tablets+and+2-in-1s+at+Amazon.com&index=8&md5=bd7acabf77a7794fa1efe2cff2e8f89a)** - check deals available on the Surface Pro 7, Surface Go, Surface Book 3 and Surface Laptop 3\\n* **[Save on Microsoft Surface Pro 8 at BHPhotoVideo.com](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Ffave.co%2F3nGrxHI&esheet=52535111&newsitemid=20211122005256&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+on+Microsoft+Surface+Pro+8+at+BHPhotoVideo.com&index=9&md5=8fe51144e7e0332c2110e74f18012843)** - view the latest deals on the 13” multi-touch Microsoft Surface Pro 8 preloaded with Windows 11\\n* **[Save up to 56% on a wide range of Microsoft Surface tablets & 2-in-1 devices at Walmart ](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qqbN21&esheet=52535111&newsitemid=20211122005256&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+up+to+56%25+on+a+wide+range+of+Microsoft+Surface+tablets+%26amp%3B+2-in-1+devices+at+Walmart&index=10&md5=5ab84dba3d4998620a7b0b5c99cb4a05)**- check the latest deals on Microsoft Surface Pro, Surface Go, Surface Book, and more\\n* **[Save on Microsoft Surface Duo phones at ATT.com](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdoqocy.com%2Fclick-9201806-14313626%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.att.com%252Fbuy%252Fphones%252Fmicrosoft-surface-duo-128gb-glacier.html&esheet=52535111&newsitemid=20211122005256&lan=en-US&anchor=Save+on+Microsoft+Surface+Duo+phones+at+ATT.com&index=11&md5=2b555347e797253353f230d1026cffd1)** - check live prices on Microsoft Surface Duo phones available in 128GB and 256GB storage capacity\\n\\nIn need of some more deals? We recommend checking **[Walmart’s Black Friday sale](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3AZLP3x&esheet=52535111&newsitemid=20211122005256&lan=en-US&anchor=Walmart%26%238217%3Bs+Black+Friday+sale&index=12&md5=c369101148bfd5b03e0b1fe46354effa)** and **[Amazon’s Black Friday page](https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&url=https%3A%2F